Use this README file to introduce your application and point to useful places in the API for learning more.
Run "rake doc:app" to generate API documentation for your models, controllers, helpers, and libraries.

Gems

Authlogic
User sessions and authentication
http://github.com/binarylogic/authlogic 

Facebooker
Facebook integration
http://github.com/mmangino/facebooker

Geokit
Geographic relationships and geographic functionality of model objects
http://github.com/andre/geokit-rails

Shoulda by Thoughtbot
Helper for writing test scripts
http://github.com/thoughtbot/shoulda


Plugins

Authlogic Facebook Connect
Integration for Facebooker and Authlogic
http://github.com/mmangino/facebooker

Delayed Job
Allows selected tasks to be run in the background
http://github.com/collectiveidea/delayed_job

Fischy Friends
Very basic setup of friend relationships
http://github.com/pogopuffin/fischyfriends

Paperclip by Thoughtbot
Image upload handling and resizing
http://github.com/thoughtbot/paperclip

Squirrel by Thoughtbot
Improved ActiveRecord search functionality
http://github.com/thoughtbot/squirrel

Will Paginate
Integrates with Squirrel to allow easy pagination
http://github.com/mislav/will_paginate

YM4R
Mapping integration for Google, Yahoo, and other mapping libraries
http://ym4r.rubyforge.org/
